Add Storage.java
commitResults.messageBody:
TommyTalks does not save tasks, causing users to restart their lists of
tasks every session.

Adding a storage class to keep track of tasks improves user-experience
since it makes the app more practical.

commitResults.messageTitle: Update Tasks to take in date and time objects
commitResults.messageBody:
Tasks track dates/times as Strings.

Let's update the app to track dates/times better so that it can track
users' tasks more accurately.
